MATCH_TOOL: Edit|Write
MATCH_PATTERN: \.claude/hooks/.*\.sh|settings\.json.*hooks
ADVISORY: |
  You are implementing or modifying a Claude Code hook.

  CRITICAL: Hook output fields have different audiences:
  - permissionDecisionReason: shown in UI ONLY — agent model NEVER sees it
  - additionalContext: injected into model context — agent sees it

  If your hook needs to advise the AGENT, use additionalContext.
  If your hook only needs to explain the decision to the USER, use permissionDecisionReason.

  This was discovered when the guardian advisory hook didn't reach agents
  until switched from permissionDecisionReason to additionalContext.
